                                    <condition>A few holes (e.g. <locus from="139" to="139" scheme="folios"/>), some with traces of stitching (e.g. <locus from="99" to="99" scheme="folios"/>, <locus from="133" to="133" scheme="folios"/>). A few larger stains around the edges (e.g. <locus from="23r" to="23r" scheme="folios"/>).</condition>
